eons and fluxons, and\n$\\rho_{xx}$ changes its behavior at $T = T_{\\rm PFS}$, reflecting the change of\nquasiparticles from chargeons and fluxons at $T < T_{\\rm PFS}$ to electrons at\n$T_{\\rm PFS} < T$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2002 20:07:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Feb 2003 05:24:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
